= Extra implementation info =

Signing and verification (as sanity check) of [https://github.com/Whonix/Whonix/blob/master/release/whonix_news whonix_news] is automated by [https://github.com/Whonix/Whonix/blob/master/release/upload_whonix_news upload_whonix_news].

[https://github.com/Whonix/Whonix/blob/master/whonix_shared/usr/lib/whonix/whonixcheck/50_check-whonix-news 50_check-whonix-news] will find out the current installing version by:

<pre>
## Read only FIRST line.
read -r INSTALLED_WHONIX_VERSION < /usr/local/share/whonix/version
## Remove ALL spaces.
INSTALLED_WHONIX_VERSION="${INSTALLED_WHONIX_VERSION//[[:space:]]}"
</pre>

While phrasing the whonix_news, it is not required to remove the OpenPGP Signature, because the function verify_whonix_news in [https://github.com/Whonix/Whonix/blob/master/whonix_shared/usr/lib/whonix/whonixcheck/50_check-whonix-news 50_check-whonix-news] will use ''gpg --decrypt'' to get plain text, which will result in the {{project name}} News File Format.

